<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="NTM8.5">
<l>vāṉkoṇṭu kiḷarnteḻunta māmukilkāḷ vēṅkaṭattut</l>
<l>tēṉkoṇṭa malarccitaṟat tiraṇṭēṟip poḻivīrkāḷ</l>
<l>ūṉkoṇṭa vaḷḷukirā liraṇiyaṉai yuṭaliṭantāṉ</l>
<l>tāṉkoṇṭa carivaḷaikaḷ tarumākil cāṟṟumiṉē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>O great clouds that spring and rise, occupying the sky!</l>
<l>O you who pour, gathering together and rising,</l>
<l rend="indent">in such a way that the honeyed flowers of Vēṅkaṭam are scattered!</l>
<l>If He who gored Hiraṇya[kaśipu]’s body with fleshy, sharp claws</l>
<l>gives [back] the slipping bracelets that He had taken away, speak [to Him]!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
